            "title": "半日收市︱亞洲稱冠 恒指半日漲504點報21419點 中概股回流憧憬助力港交所",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">環球貿易戰暫呈拉鋸，未助股市反彈，港股今早表現更亞洲主要股市中稱冠；中概股或回流，則為港交所(00388)添加動力。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：港交所官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250203_FI_source-web_00388-CNY-4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：港交所官網影片截圖\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250203_FI_source-web_00388-CNY-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：港交所官網影片截圖</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數今早跟隨外圍裂口跳升，甫開市即重越100天線(最新約為21209點)，開報21363點，飆449點，初段升幅雖然曾收窄，但半日低位仍達21224點，升309點，上午10時過後升幅一直在350點之上，最高曾見21517點，升602點；恒指中午收報21419點，升504點或2.41%。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：港交所官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250203_FI_source-web_00388-CNY-4.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：港交所官網影片截圖\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250203_FI_source-web_00388-CNY-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：港交所官網影片截圖</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：港交所官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/00388-5.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：港交所官網影片截圖\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/00388-5.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：港交所官網影片截圖</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：友邦官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20230821_FI_source-web_友邦2.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：友邦官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20230821_FI_source-web_友邦2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：友邦官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230703-101726__source-web_09988-9_source-web_-1.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230703-101726__source-web_09988-9_source-web_-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"潼關黃金2024年度中期報告封面\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/00340-2024.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"潼關黃金2024年度中期報告封面\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/00340-2024.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">潼關黃金2024年度中期報告封面</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：港交所官網影片截圖\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250203_FI_source-web_00388-CNY-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：港交所官網影片截圖</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：港交所官網影片截圖\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/00388-5.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：港交所官網影片截圖</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：友邦官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20230821_FI_source-web_友邦2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：友邦官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230703-101726__source-web_09988-9_source-web_-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"潼關黃金2024年度中期報告封面\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/00340-2024.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">潼關黃金2024年度中期報告封面</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數稍微跑贏大市，半日升131點或2.69%，報5032點；國企指數升168點或2.16%，報7970點。主板半日成交1542.59億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指半日升566點，報21422點，高水2點。科指期貨升154點，報5042點，高水10點。國指期貨升195點，報7969點，低水1點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：港交所官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/00388-5.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：港交所官網影片截圖\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/00388-5.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：港交所官網影片截圖</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港交所成為今早升市主要功臣之一，裂口高開逾2.5%後拾級向上，最高曾衝上336元，升7.55%；中午收報334.8元，仍漲22.4元或7.17%，登上藍籌升幅榜首。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股交投持續暢旺，本已利好港交所前景，而中美雙方在關稅問題持續爭拗，有傳美國總統特朗普或以將美國上市的中概股除牌作為博奕籌碼，或引發中概股回流，屆持香港有望成為這些回流中概念的首選，相關憧憬成為利好港交所的另一因素。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">除了港交所外，重磅金融股與科股也今早推動港股的火車頭。近年持續回購的滙控(00005)，其ADR往往逆市造好，該股今早更跑贏大市，半日升3.31%，報78元；友邦(01299)上月中宣布的16億美元回購方案，剛於上周與券商訂立全權運作計畫，該股今早亦漲4.19%，報52.25元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：友邦官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20230821_FI_source-web_友邦2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：友邦官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20230821_FI_source-web_友邦2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：友邦官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">兩大重磅科股阿里巴巴(09988)與騰訊(00700)同樣跑贏大市，當中以阿里巴巴表現尤其突出，最高曾見109.9元，漲6.7%；中午收報108.7元，仍升5.7元或5.53%，在藍籌升幅榜居次席，並以111.69億元交投成為主板成交額榜首。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">騰訊表現也絕不失禮，最多曾升3.66%，高見459.2元；中午收報456.8元，升13.4元或3.02%，半日成交也達88.76億元。單是騰訊、阿里巴巴、港交所、滙控及友邦5隻股份，合共已為恒指進賬364點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230703-101726__source-web_09988-9_source-web_-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230703-101726__source-web_09988-9_source-web_-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">金價揚升，則推動金礦與金飾零售股炒上。紫金礦業(02899)升4.84%，報17.34元；早前獲紫金入股的潼關黃金(00340)更飆18.33%，報1.42元；赤峰黃金(06693)漲9.91%，報23.85元，破頂創下歷史新高；山東黃金(01787)升7.39%，報21.8元，也見3年高位；靈寶黃金(03330)升4.51%，報9.04元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"潼關黃金2024年度中期報告封面\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/00340-2024.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"潼關黃金2024年度中期報告封面\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/00340-2024.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">潼關黃金2024年度中期報告封面</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">金飾零售股方面，周大福(01929)升4.19%，報9.45元；老鋪黃金(06181)漲10.03%，報817.5元；金貓銀貓(01815)飆15.32%，報1.43元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14852894-%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e4%ba%9e%e6%b4%b2%e7%a8%b1%e5%86%a0-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e6%bc%b2504%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b121419%e9%bb%9e-%e4%b8%ad%e6%a6%82%e8%82%a1%e5%9b%9e",
