        {
            "title": "A股半日升  貿易數據勝預期",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股半日升，出口數據勝預期，兩市合計成交8387.75億元(人民幣‧下同)。 </p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20230629_FI_A股_9_source-ap_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20230629_FI_A股_9_source-ap_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指半日收報3266點，升27點或0.86%，今早上證綜指以3251點開市，升13點或0.42%。最低見3244點，升6點或0.19%，即反覆向上，最高見3272點，升34點或1.05%，為上午高位，半日成交3538.17億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指半日升89點或0.91%，報9923點，今日開市報9955點，更漲121點或1.23%，最高見9964點，升130點或1.32%，其後回落，最低見9879點，跌0.46%或45點，半日成交4849.58億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數半日報3768點，升17點或0.47%，今日開升21點或0.57%，開報3772點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數半日升15點或0.82%，報1942點，今早開市報1954點，升27點或1.44%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國3月以美元計價出口按年升12.4%，貿易順差1026.4億美元，均超過預期。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14852821-a%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e5%8d%87-%e8%b2%bf%e6%98%93%e6%95%b8%e6%93%9a%e5%8b%9d%e9%a0%90%e6%9c%9f",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20181030_FI_A-SHARES__FB-3_source-ap_.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-14 11:45:34",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "中國3月以美元計價出口按年升12.4% 貿易順差1026.4億美元 均超預期",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">海關總署數據顯示，中國3月份按美元計出口按年增12.4%，貿易順差達1026.4億美元，兩者均遠超預期。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240808_FI_source-ap_China_Trade-4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240808_FI_source-ap_China_Trade-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">根據海關總署公布的最新數據，以美元計，3月份中國進出口總值達5251.8億美元，按年升5%。其中出口總值3139.1億美元，按年升12.4%；進口總值12112.7億美元，按年減少4.3%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">若將今年首3個月累計，進出口總值1.43萬億美元，按年微升0.2。出口總值8536.7億美元，按年升5.8%；進口總值5807億美元，按年減少7%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14852714-%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b3%e6%9c%88%e4%bb%a5%e7%be%8e%e5%85%83%e8%a8%88%e5%83%b9%e5%87%ba%e5%8f%a3%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%8d%8712-4-%e8%b2%bf%e6%98%93%e9%a0%86%e5%b7%ae1026-4%e5%84%84%e7%be%8e%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_China_Trump_Tariffs_25097543963940-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-14 11:20:38",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "現貨金再創新高",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">現貨金再創新高，一度高見每盎司3245.42美元，較早時報3233.85美元，跌幅近0.1%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">紐約期金較早時報3249.5美元，升幅約0.2%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14852636-%e7%8f%be%e8%b2%a8%e9%87%91%e5%86%8d%e5%89%b5%e6%96%b0%e9%ab%98",
